graph TD
    A[User Clicks OK] --> B[Dialog Validates Views]
    B --> C{First Field Valid?}
    C -->|Yes| D{Next Field Valid?}
    C -->|No| E[Focus First Field]
    D -->|Yes| F{More Fields?}
